                    </span>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="foundation-card" style="position: relative;">
                <button class="lang-toggle-btn" data-target="vision" style="position: absolute; top: 16px; right: 16px; border: none; background: #f1f1f1; border-radius: 50%; width: 36px; height: 36px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer;">EN</button>
